<P><NOTE PLACE="marg">Exo. xx. Deut. v<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></NOTE>Why do not these wretches call this precepte of God to theyr reme~bra~s, Thou shalt not take the name of the Lorde thy GOD in vayne. For the Lorde wyll not holde hym gyltles, y^t taketh his name in vayne. The wis<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> man also saythe, A man that vsethe
