<P>It is to be noted, that the Scrip+ture calleth y^t a blissed hope, wherw^t we hope and looke for the glorious commyng of oure Lorde &amp; sauioure Iesus Christ vnto the iudgemente. And not w^tout a cause. For althogh a Christen man be neuer so greatly vexed in thys worlde, yet whan he
